## Partial type

A partial has all methods of the Node but no data values. It can be used in the same was as an Observable. A full node will be created by waiting for the promise of by reading the node. TODO: Write/review documentation

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type Partial<Node> = Observable<Node> & Pick<Node, MethodKeys<Node>>;
```
